\PYG{g+gu}{subsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.0 Axiomatisation de la mecanique harmonique du chaos discret\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{text}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{l+s}{  La configuration geometrique fondamentale repose sur une famille de carres}
\PYG{l+s}{  embo\PYGZbs{}\PYGZca{}ites, tous alignes avec les axes du plan cartesien et partageant le point}
\PYG{l+s}{  commun A = (0,0). Le carre de niveau n possede un cote de longueur 1.5\PYGZca{}n,}
\PYG{l+s}{  ce qui correspond exactement aux elevations visibles dans la figure TikZ :}

\PYG{l+s}{      1.5\PYGZca{}1, 1.5\PYGZca{}2, 1.5\PYGZca{}3, 1.5\PYGZca{}4, ..., 1.5\PYGZca{}n.}

\PYG{l+s}{  Dans chaque carre de niveau n est inscrit un triangle isocele dont le sommet}
\PYG{l+s}{  superieur est le point C(n) = (1.5\PYGZca{}n, 1.5\PYGZca{}n), et dont la base repose sur les}
\PYG{l+s}{  axes de coordonnees. La base est constituee des deux points :}

\PYG{l+s}{      P1(n,p) = (b(n,p), 0)}
\PYG{l+s}{      P2(n,p) = (0, b(n,p))}

\PYG{l+s}{  ou b(n,p) est une longueur strictement positive dependant du niveau n et du}
\PYG{l+s}{  nombre premier p.}

\PYG{l+s}{  Lorsque la diagonale AC(n) coupe la base du triangle inscrit, celui\PYGZhy{}ci est}
\PYG{l+s}{  divise en deux triangles rectangles. Dans chacun de ces triangles rectangles,}
\PYG{l+s}{  la demi\PYGZhy{}base vaut b(n,p)/2 et la hauteur vaut h(n,p). Le rapport geometrique}
\PYG{l+s}{  fondamental de la m\PYGZbs{}\PYGZsq{}ecanique harmonique du chaos discret est :}

\PYG{l+s}{      (b(n,p) / 2) / h(n,p) = sqrt(p)}

\PYG{l+s}{  ou p est un nombre premier d\PYGZbs{}\PYGZsq{}efinissant l\PYGZsq{}unit\PYGZbs{}\PYGZsq{}e admissible.}

\PYG{l+s}{  Ce rapport ne concerne donc pas le triangle complet, mais le demi\PYGZhy{}triangle}
\PYG{l+s}{  rectangle issu de la coupure par la diagonale AC(n). Ce point est essentiel :}
\PYG{l+s}{  c\PYGZsq{}est ce demi\PYGZhy{}triangle rectangle qui porte l\PYGZsq{}information geometrique}
\PYG{l+s}{  fondamentale de l\PYGZsq{}unit\PYGZbs{}\PYGZsq{}e p.}

\PYG{l+s}{  Le rapport ci\PYGZhy{}dessus determine l\PYGZsq{}angle theta(p) du triangle rectangle par :}

\PYG{l+s}{      tan(theta(p)) = sqrt(p)}
\PYG{l+s}{      theta(p) = arctan(sqrt(p))}

\PYG{l+s}{  Cet angle joue un role central dans les chapitres B et C, notamment dans la}
\PYG{l+s}{  matrice \PYGZbs{}`a derive premiere et dans la structure du prisme matriciel.}
\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{g+gu}{subsubsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.1 Unites admissibles\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{prime\PYGZus{}nat}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat \PYGZbs{}Rightarrow bool\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}prime\PYGZus{}nat p \PYGZbs{}longleftrightarrow (p \PYGZgt{} 1 \PYGZbs{}wedge (\PYGZbs{}forallm. m dvd p \PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZgt{} m = 1 \PYGZbs{}vee m = p))\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{admissible\PYGZus{}unit}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat \PYGZbs{}Rightarrow bool\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}admissible\PYGZus{}unit p \PYGZbs{}longleftrightarrow prime\PYGZus{}nat p\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{unit}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}unit p = sqrt (real p) + 1\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{g+gu}{subsubsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.2 Carr\PYGZbs{}\PYGZsq{}es embo\PYGZbs{}\PYGZca{}it\PYGZbs{}\PYGZsq{}es\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{type\PYGZus{}synonym}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{point}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}real \PYGZbs{}times real\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{side}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}side n = (1.5 :: real) \PYGZca{} n\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{A}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{point}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A = (0,0)\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{B}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat \PYGZbs{}Rightarrow point\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}B n = (side n, 0)\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{C}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat \PYGZbs{}Rightarrow point\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}C n = (side n, side n)\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{D}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat \PYGZbs{}Rightarrow point\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}D n = (0, side n)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{g+gu}{subsubsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.3 Triangles inscrits\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{text}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{l+s}{  Le triangle inscrit dans le carre de niveau n et associe a l\PYGZsq{}unite p possede}
\PYG{l+s}{  les sommets :}

\PYG{l+s}{      C(n), P1(n,p), P2(n,p)}

\PYG{l+s}{  ou la base repose sur les axes et le sommet est C(n).}
\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{base\PYGZus{}param}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}base\PYGZus{}param n p = (side n) / (sqrt (real p) + 0.5)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{P1}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} nat =\PYGZgt{} point\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}P1 n p = (base\PYGZus{}param n p, 0)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{P2}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} nat =\PYGZgt{} point\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}P2 n p = (0, base\PYGZus{}param n p)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{g+gu}{subsubsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.4 Rapport fondamental : demi\PYGZhy{}base / hauteur = sqrt(p)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{dist2}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}point =\PYGZgt{} point =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}dist2 P Q = sqrt ((fst P \PYGZhy{} fst Q)\PYGZca{}2 + (snd P \PYGZhy{} snd Q)\PYGZca{}2)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{base\PYGZus{}length}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}base\PYGZus{}length n p = dist2 (P1 n p) (P2 n p)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{height\PYGZus{}length}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}height\PYGZus{}length n p =}
\PYG{l+s}{     abs ((2 * side n \PYGZhy{} base\PYGZus{}param n p) / sqrt 2)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{ratio\PYGZus{}halfbase\PYGZus{}height}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}ratio\PYGZus{}halfbase\PYGZus{}height n p =}
\PYG{l+s}{     ((base\PYGZus{}length n p) / 2) / (height\PYGZus{}length n p)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{axiomatization}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n}{ratio\PYGZus{}axiom}\PYG{o}{:}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}admissible\PYGZus{}unit p ==\PYGZgt{} n \PYGZgt{}= 1}
\PYG{l+s}{     ==\PYGZgt{} ratio\PYGZus{}halfbase\PYGZus{}height n p = sqrt (real p)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{g+gu}{subsubsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.5 Angle associe a l\PYGZsq{}unite p\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{angle\PYGZus{}rect}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}angle\PYGZus{}rect p = arctan (sqrt (real p))\PYGZdq{}}


\PYG{g+gu}{subsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}B2.0 Angle oppose dans le demi\PYGZhy{}triangle rectangle\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{text}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{l+s}{  Lorsque la diagonale AC coupe la base du triangle inscrit, celui\PYGZhy{}ci est divise}
\PYG{l+s}{  en deux triangles rectangles. Dans chacun de ces triangles rectangles, la}
\PYG{l+s}{  demi\PYGZhy{}base vaut b/2 et la hauteur vaut h. Le rapport geometrique fondamental est :}

\PYG{l+s}{      (b / 2) / h = sqrt(p)}

\PYG{l+s}{  L\PYGZsq{}angle oppose a la demi\PYGZhy{}base est donc :}

\PYG{l+s}{      theta(p) = arctan(sqrt(p))}

\PYG{l+s}{  Cette fonction joue un role central dans la matrice a derive premiere.}
\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}


\PYG{g+gu}{subsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}B2.1 Angle oppose pour la matrice a derive premiere\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{text}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{l+s}{  Nous reutilisons la fonction angle\PYGZus{}rect definie dans le Chapitre A.}
\PYG{l+s}{  Elle encode l\PYGZsq{}angle du demi\PYGZhy{}triangle rectangle associe a l\PYGZsq{}unite p.}
\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k+kn}{lemma}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{angle\PYGZus{}rect\PYGZus{}prime}\PYG{o}{:}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k+kp}{assumes}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}prime\PYGZus{}nat p\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k+kp}{shows}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}angle\PYGZus{}rect p = arctan (sqrt (real p))\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{by}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{(}\PYG{n}{simp}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{add}\PYG{o}{:}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{angle\PYGZus{}rect\PYGZus{}def}\PYG{o}{)}


\PYG{g+gu}{subsubsection}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}A1.6 Unite geometrique via le segment AL\PYGZus{}nat\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{text}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{l+s}{  On definit le segment AL\PYGZus{}nat(p) de maniere a ce que l\PYGZsq{}unite geometrique :}

\PYG{l+s}{      U(p) = sqrt 4.5 / AL\PYGZus{}nat(p)}

\PYG{l+s}{  soit egale a l\PYGZsq{}unite abstraite sqrt p + 1.}

\PYG{l+s}{  On obtient :}

\PYG{l+s}{      AL\PYGZus{}nat(p) = sqrt 4.5 / (sqrt p + 1).}
\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{AL\PYGZus{}nat}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}AL\PYGZus{}nat p = sqrt 4.5 / (sqrt (real p) + 1)\PYGZdq{}}

\PYG{k}{definition}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{geometric\PYGZus{}unit}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{::}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}nat =\PYGZgt{} real\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k+kp}{where}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}geometric\PYGZus{}unit p = sqrt 4.5 / AL\PYGZus{}nat p\PYGZdq{}}


\PYG{k+kn}{lemma}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n}{geometric\PYGZus{}unit\PYGZus{}eq\PYGZus{}unit}\PYG{o}{:}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k+kp}{assumes}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s}{\PYGZdq{}AL\PYGZus{}nat p \PYGZti{}= 0\PYGZdq{}}
